data.text:
USS KVPV Solar LLC CSG is ranked #275 out of 477 solar farms in Minnesota in terms of total annual net electricity generation.

USS KVPV Solar LLC CSG generated 447.0 MWh during the 3-month period between September 2023 to December 2023.
